 frequencies are twice as high. We show that\nvariation of the accretion rate leads to drift of the QPO peak.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Dec 2008 20:57:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Dec 2008 21:00:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Dec 2008 20:54:40 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2009 17:00:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
