et at z<0.5, but this value may increase when bias\nand incompleteness are taken into account and help close the gap on the 50% of\nthe baryons still \"missing\".\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Dec 2008 21:51:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
